> could I ask what is the scene to be used？

@ni-ze 
To collect logs from some Android apps and send them to the server in a simple way without having to build an entire logging platform. Using MQ is a good choice at this time, and the client can directly integrate Rocketmq’s Client to achieve this. Most companies have existing MQ services.This is an idea I had to send logs in a lazy way.

